174
00:09:28,035 --> 00:09:29,894
So, who was this guy?

175
00:09:29,894 --> 00:09:31,619
Worked in the music store.

176
00:09:31,619 --> 00:09:33,268
I guess they met at the food court.

177
00:09:33,268 --> 00:09:34,650
Do you remember a name?

178
00:09:34,650 --> 00:09:37,697
You know, I want to say Max, uh...

179
00:09:37,697 --> 00:09:41,289
but it was a pretty long time ago.

180
00:09:42,095 --> 00:09:44,281
Mark has this girl up on a pedestal.

181
00:09:44,281 --> 00:09:47,255
She was everything to him, his one and only.

182
00:09:47,255 --> 00:09:49,027
