201
00:10:31,717 --> 00:10:33,698
What did you think of 
her boyfriend Mark?

202
00:10:33,698 --> 00:10:36,607
Nice. Especially for a rich kid.

203
00:10:36,607 --> 00:10:37,922
He treat Eve okay?

204
00:10:37,922 --> 00:10:40,108
Yes, called about four times a night.

205
00:10:40,108 --> 00:10:41,725
Like he was checking up on her?

206
